In [761]:
def dms2dd(s):
    try:
        degrees, minutes, direction = re.split('[\'"]+', s)
        dd = float(degrees) + float(minutes)/60
        if direction in ('S','W'):
            dd*= -1
        return dd
    except:
        return s


def Preprocessing(filename):
    
    df=pd.read_excel(filename,skiprows=3,nrows=33)
    df.columns = ['GDH', 'Rang', 'Voile', 'Skipper/Bateau', 'Heure', 'Lat', 'Long', 
         'Cap_30', 'Vitesse_30', 'VMG_30', 'Distance_30',
         'Cap_last', 'Vitesse_last', 'VMG_last', 'Distance_last',
         'Cap_24', 'Vitesse_24', 'VMG_24', 'Distance_24', 
         'DTF', 'DTL']
    df=df.drop(0)
    #df=df.dropna()
    df = df.dropna(axis=1, how="all")
    
    #Nettoyge de la colonne voile/Nationalit
    df["Voile"]=df["Voile"].str.split('\n').str[1]
    #apply(lambda x: x[-1] if isinstance(x,list) else x).apply(to_numeric())
    df.insert(3,"nat",df["Voile"].str.split(' ').apply(lambda x: x[0] if isinstance(x,list) else x))
    df["Voile"]=df["Voile"].str.split(' ').apply(lambda x: x[1] if isinstance(x,list) else x).astype(float)
    
    #Nettoayage de la colonne Skipper/Bateau
    df["Skipper/Bateau"].str.split("\n").apply(lambda x: x[0] if isinstance(x,list) else x)
    df.insert(5,"Bateau",df["Skipper/Bateau"].str.split("\n").apply(lambda x: x[1] if isinstance(x,list) else x))
    df["Skipper/Bateau"]=df["Skipper/Bateau"].str.split("\n").apply(lambda x: x[0] if isinstance(x,list) else x)
    df=df.rename(columns={'Skipper/Bateau':'Nom du skipper'})
    
    #Formattage de la collone Heure
    date = re.search('([0-9]{8})', "20201108_140000.xlsx").group(0)
    df['Heure'] = df['Heure'].apply(lambda x: datetime.datetime.strptime(date+'_'+x[:5], '%Y%m%d_%H:%M') if  isinstance(x,str) else x)

    
    #convertir les colonnes numriques en donnes exploitables(sans units)
    num_cols = list(df.columns[8:])
    df[num_cols] = df[num_cols].apply(lambda x: x.astype(str).str.replace(re.compile('[a-z]+|'), '')).apply(pd.to_numeric)
    
    df['Lat']=df['Lat'].apply(dms2dd)
    df['Long']=df['Long'].apply(dms2dd)
                                        
    df.iloc[:,8:] = df.iloc[:,8:].astype('float')
    return df

def load_data_final():
    
    #On cre un dataframe qui contient lle classement final
    df_final = pd.read_excel("20210305_080000.xlsx",skiprows=4,nrows=33,header=[0])
    df_final = df_final.dropna(axis=1, how="all")
    df_final.columns=[ 'Rang final', 'Numro de voile', 'Skipper/Bateau'
                             ,"Date d'arriv", 'Temps de course',
                              'Ecart au premier',
                             'Ecart au prcdent', "Vitesse sur l'ortho","Distance sur l'ortho",'pourcentage',
                             'Vitesse sur le fond','Distance sur le fond']

    df_final.insert(2, 'Nom du skipper', df_final['Skipper/Bateau'].str.split('\n').str[0])
    df_final.insert(3, 'Nom du bateau', df_final['Skipper/Bateau'].str.split('\n').str[1])
    df_final = df_final.drop(['Skipper/Bateau'],axis=1)
    df_final['Numro de voile'] = df_final['Numro de voile'].str.split('\n').str[1]
    df_final['Rang final'] = df_final['Rang final'].str.split('\n').str[0]
    df_final = df_final.replace('\n',' :',regex=True)
    df_final.drop(df_final[df_final.iloc[:,0] == 'RET' ].index , inplace=True)    
    df_final.iloc[:,0] = df_final.iloc[:,0].astype('int')
    df_final.iloc[:,8:] = df_final.iloc[:,8:].replace(r'[^\d\.]', '',regex=True)
    df_final.iloc[:,8:] = df_final.iloc[:,8:].astype('float')
    
    return df_final

def load_boats_data():
    soup = BeautifulSoup(requests.get("https://www.vendeeglobe.org/fr/glossaire").content.decode("utf-8"))
    boats=list()
    for boat in soup.find_all("div", {"class":"boats-list__popup-infos"}):
        dict_ = {"nom":boat.find("h3").text}
        for li in boat.find_all("li")[:-1]:
            dict_[li.text.split(":")[0].strip()] = li.text.split(":")[1].strip()
        boats.append(dict_)
    df_boats = pd.DataFrame(boats)
    
    
    for col in df_boats.columns:
        df_boats[col] = df_boats[col].str.lower()
        
    df_boats["Foils"] = df_boats["Nombre de drives"].map({"foiler":"foils","2":"no foils","2 asymtriques":"no foils","foils":"foils"})
    df_boats = df_boats.drop("Nombre de drives",1)

    df_boats["Voile quille"] = df_boats["Voile quille"].apply(lambda x: x.split()[0] if isinstance(x,str) else x)

    df_boats["Numro de voile"] = df_boats["Numro de voile"].fillna(59) 

    df_boats["Year_launched"] = df_boats["Date de lancement"].apply(lambda x: x[-4:])
    df_boats["Year_launched"] = pd.to_datetime(df_boats["Year_launched"], format="%Y").dt.year
    df_boats = df_boats.drop("Date de lancement",1)

    my_cols = ["Numro de voile","Tirant d'eau","Dplacement (poids)","Longueur","Largeur","Surface de voiles au prs", "Hauteur mt"]
    for col in my_cols:
        df_boats[col] = df_boats[col].apply(lambda x: re.sub("[a-z]+", "", str(x).lower()).strip().replace(",","."))
    df_boats["Numro de voile"] = df_boats["Numro de voile"].astype(int).replace(16,10).replace(77,777) 
    df_boats["Dplacement (poids)"] = df_boats["Dplacement (poids)"].apply(lambda x: np.nan if x == "" else x)
    df_boats["Surface de voiles au prs"] = df_boats["Surface de voiles au prs"].apply(lambda x: x.split()[0])
    df_boats[my_cols] = df_boats[my_cols].astype(float)
    
    return df_boats


df_boats = load_boats_data()
